# door — in-room door, openable, auto reverse exit

room West "West room."

    door wooden door "A plain wooden door."
        east: East
        is openable.

room East "East room."

test "default"
    east. "You can't, since the wooden door is in the way."
    open wooden door. "You open"
    east. "East room"
    west. "West room"
